    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK579">
<l>oruttāṟṟum paṇpiṉār kaṇṇuṅkaṇ ṇōṭip </l>
<l>poṟuttāṟṟum paṇpē talai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Patiently to bear with, and show kindness to those who grieve us, is the most excellent of all dispositions.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
